name: 2021 Collector Thank You
description:
Starting my digital artistic journey in September of 2021, the journey so far has been a delightful creative ride within an amazingly supportive community, which I’m happy to be a part of - Here's to the end of 2021 and looking forward to 2022!

As of Dec 30, 2021 @ 6:45PM,  I've had the honour of being collected by 163 distinct and unique collectors out there in the Tezos blockchain. I sincerely appreciate all your support and as such here is a token of my appreciation.
